.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=1cebe827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span></strong>"}]}